## How It Works

The Analytics component will:
- Automatically track page views when users navigate between routes
- Send analytics data to Vercel's `/_vercel/insights/` endpoints
- Work seamlessly with the React Router setup (BrowserRouter)
- Only send data when deployed to Vercel (no local tracking in development)

## Next Steps for Deployment

To enable analytics data collection:

1. Deploy the application to Vercel using `vercel deploy`
2. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard:
   - Go to your project dashboard
   - Click the "Analytics" tab
   - Click "Enable" to activate tracking
3. After deployment, verify tracking by:
   - Visiting your deployed site
   - Opening browser DevTools Network tab
   - Looking for requests to `/_vercel/insights/view`

